data.description: Located in the peaceful neighborhood of Citrus Hill, Meadowview. This large 2 bedroom, 2 bath home is ready for you to make it your own! With just over 2200 sqft of living space there is tons of room for entertaining or throwing perfect pool party! Inside you'll find a formal living room and dining room with a wood burning fireplace. The master bedroom offers space for a sitting room or office with sliding glass doors leading to the pool deck. The master bathroom features dual sinks, walk-in closet and titled shower. The kitchen boasts granite counter top, a large island, newer appliances, farm style sink and tons of windows facing the pool bar. The great room would make for a sound studio, theatre room or game room- the possibilities are endless. Outside you have an acre of land, spa, pool and shed. The pool deck is covered in pavers and screened in. There is also a tiki bar and another bar top running along the kitchen windows. There is even a sauna! You don't want to miss this one! Schedule your showing today!
